    {
      "id": "1944750c-f3ba-80ec-963e-c45c19af9678",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Traditional learning has the drawback of being a one-size fits all solution where, despite their differences, all learners follow the same path → and the materials usually recommended follow this linear approach to learning, which may hamper a student’s performance. And, while there is literature on personalizing learning, most of it ignores relationship between concepts or difficulty (focusing on preferences).",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1944750c-f3ba-80ec-963e-c45c19af9678",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
          "page_id": "36a4d513-0524-49db-acaa-e337f29073e7"
        },
        "created_time": "2025-02-08T21:52:00.000Z",
        "last_edited_time": "2025-02-08T21:55:00.000Z",
