    {
      "id": "1944750c-f3ba-807e-8de8-e0b27b978cc7",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The paper uses a Genetic-Algorithm based model that aims to generate optimized learning pathways that account for these constraints. Results show that the quality of the GA approach is higher than traditional learning paths.",
